data.text: Two huge things happened in Uzbekistan fintech market this year. Earlier this year, we learned that Payme's remaining shares (controlling shares) were acquired by TBC. Last week we all learned that Click is merging with Uzum. There are lots of questions. Has Uzum bought Click? Has Click bought Uzum? Is this a merger? Will we still have our favorite app? Over the last 12 years, Click has become a verb. In US we say: "Venmo me or Zelle me" In Uzbekistan we say: "Click me some money". The guest of episode 12 of Techstans pod is Click CEO Ulug'bek Rustamov. We tried to cover all questions that our listeners forwarded us. If you want to learn about the biggest deal in Uzbekistan fintech market, go to comments and listen to our podcast on your favorite platform. #fintech #clickuzbekistan #uzum
